Mumiriri weMbizo mudare reparamende vari nhengo yeCCC VaSettlement Chikwinya vanoti matikitivha ange achiongoriora nyaya yekupondwa kwenhengo yebato ravo VaMboneni Ncube vakaendeswa kune mamwe matunhu mushure mekusunga vanofungidzirwa kuti vatsigiri veZanu-PF vainge vachipomerwa mhosva yekuvaponda.
Hatina kukwanisa kubata mutauriri wemapurisa Assistant commissioner Paul Nyathi kana mukuru mubazi rezvekuburitswa kwemashoko muZanu-PF VaTafadzwa Mugwadi sezvo vange vasiri kudaira nharembozha dzavo. Asi vaviri ava vanogara vachiti mapurisa haatarise kuti wabuda mumba maani.
Mapurisa akasunga vanhu gumi nevatanhatu vaipomerwa mhosva yekupinda VaNcube asi gumi nemumwe vakasungunurwa kukasara vashanu vanoti Edmore Shoshera, 30, Albert Maketo Tembo, 29, Percy Mukwaturi, 38, Talent Imbayago, 28, na Panashe Makuvaza.
Mutungamiri webato rinopikisa reCitizens Coalition for Change VaNelson Chamisa vaita musangano muKwekwe nhasi kunyangwe paine mashoko ekuti imwe nhengo yavo yakawohwa nezuro nevanofungidzirwa kuti vatsigiri veZanu-PF vaida kutyisidzira vanhu kuti vasaende kumusangano uyu.
Musangano wanhasi wange wakanangana nekutenda vatsigiri vebato iri nekurivhotera musarudzo dzemaby elections muna Kurume. Bato reCCC riri kutiwo kumhan’ara nyaya dzemhirizhonga kumapurisa kwave kunetsa sezvo naivo vave kutyisidzirwa nevakuru muhurumende nekuendeswa kune mamwe makamba vakaongorora nyaya idzi.
Source : Voa

4. Unogona kupa OEM masevhisi?
Ehe, isu tinopa maOEM masevhisi zvichienderana neiyo OEN dhizaini.
5. Chii chinonzi kubhadhara?
Unogona kutibhadhara kuburikidza neT/T, LC, PayPal uye Western Union.
6. Chii chinonzi nguva yekufambisa?
Tichakutumira zvinhu pakarepo mushure mekugamuchira mubhadharo wakakwana.
7. Mutengo nechokufambisa chii?
Inogona kuva FOB, CFR uye CIF mitengo, tinogona kubatsira vatengi kuronga zvikepe.

Ruambamabari
Ruambamabari (Genetics) chidzidzo chemabvumbo eropa, chinowongorora kufanana nekusiyana kuripo pakati pezvinyanhengo zvine hukama, izvi zvichibva pakupishingana kwenharaunda inoraramirwa nemabari ezvinorarama.
Mamwe Mazwi[chinja | edit source]
- Chibaranye (Genome).
- Baranyera (Genomics). (Genomics study of the structure, function, evolution, and mapping of genomes).
- Mabari (Genes) - pahuwandu ndiro izwi rimwe.
Kupiwa kweZita[chinja | edit source]
- Chivakashure ruamba chiri kushandiswa kuturikira chivakamberi logy chinowanikwa kuEnglish mumazwi anodudza zvidzidzo zvnoti: biology, geology, physiology etc.
- Chivakamberi cheEnglish chekuti -logy chinoreva a speaking, discourse, treatise, doctrine, theory, science".
- Geneticist rinenge roturikirwa kunzi chiambamabari.

etwork (ZESN) Amai Ellen Dingani vatiwo sangano ravo richirikuongorora gwaro redelimitation iri uye vachazotaura nesu kana vapedza kuongorora gwaro rese.

Kechipiri, iyo yakakosha zviratidzo zvekutarisa inogona zvakare kuratidza BP (BP), kusanganisira systolic (SYS) uye diastolic blood pressure (DIA).
Yakajairika kukosha kwe systolic blood pressure i90-140mmH

SANGANO rakazvimirira reHard Mashona Arts and Culture Trust roshanda pamwe chete nevaimbi vemisambo yakasiyana mukusimudzira matarenda evechidiki munyaya dzemimhanzi pamwe neutano hwavo. Muhurukuro nemukuru wesangano iri,
“Tichange happy wheels tichiita mashoo nevaimbi vakasiyana vanosanganisira vechitendero neveZim-dancehall tichitsvaga mari yekuvandudza hupenyu hwevechidiki vane zvirwere zvinoda kunovhiiwa kunze kunyika dzakaita seIndia,” anodaro.
Anoenderera mberi achiti, “Mukana uyu tichaupa zvakare vechidiki avo vane matarenda ekuimba patichange tichifamba mapurovhinzi ese tichitenderera Zimbabwe. Donzvo redu nderekusimudzira vechidiki vane matarenda ekuimba nekunyora nziyo.”
Anoti zvinorwadza kuona kuti kune vamwe vechidiki vane zvipo zvinokwanisa kuti vawane raramo muhupenyu hwavo asi vari kushaya rutsigiro ruzere.
“Kune vechidiki vane matarenda ezvekuimba vari kushaya zvakare vari kuvabatsira zvinova zvinoita kuti vamwe vacho vazowanikwe vave kuputa nekunwa zvinodhaka,” anodaro Musoni.

Vadzidzi vemuzvikoro zvepamusoro vanoti havafanirwe kubhadhara mari dzechikoro apo vanenge vachishanda basa rezvavanenge vachidzidzira.
Vadzidzi ava vanoti vanopedzesera vobhadhara mari yakawandisa nekuda kwekuti vanenge vachifanirwa kutsvaga mari yezvekufambisa kuenda kubasa kwavasingabhadharwe uye pekugara sezvo vasingawane basa munzvimbo dzavanogara.
Mumwe mudzidzi wepachikoro chikuru cheMidlands State University, VaArthur Bwanya, vanoti havafanirwe kunge vachibhadhara mari dzechikoro sezvo vasinga bhadharwe apo vanenge vachishanda.
VaBwanya vanoti vanopedzesera vobhadhara mari yakawandisa sezvo vachifanirwa kuzviriritira kubasa kwavanenge vachishanda.
VaBwanya vanoti mari yavari kubhadhara vari pa attachment yakawandisa iyo vanoti inongoshanda kuti vaziviswe kuti vakabudirira here kana kuti kwete paattachment.
Mumwe mudzidzi wepaChinhoyi University of Technology, CUT, VaTinashe Kawanzaruwa, vanoti havaone zvichikodzera kuti vabhadhare mari vari pa attachment sezvo panenge pasina midziyo yechikoro yavanenge vachishandisa.
Vachitaura pavaishanya neChina paCUT gurukota redzidzo yepamusoro, VaAmon Murwira, vakati hurumende haina hurongwa hwekumisa kubhadharwa kwemari yedzidzo nevadzidzi vanenge vari paattachment sezvo ichishandiswa mukufamba nekugara mumahotera kwevadzidzisi vanoongorora vadzidzi ava pavanenge vachishanda.
Izvi ndizvo zviri kurambwa nevadzidzi ava vachiti zvinhu hazvina kumira zvakanaka munyika, izvo zviri kuita kuti vanhu vaomerwe nehupenyu.

Zinc oxide Varistor
Metal oxide Varistor / Zinc oxide Varistor haina-mutsetse resistor inoshandisa semiconductor electrocnic zvedongo chinhu chinonyanya kuumbwa ne zinc oxide. Inodaidzwa kuti varistor kana mental oxide varistor (MOV), sezvazvinoenderana nekuchinja kwemagetsi. Muviri wevaristor chimiro chematriki chinoumbwa neinc oxide particles. Iyo miganhu yezviyo pakati pezvimedu yakafanana neyakafanana magetsi emagetsi enzira mbiri dzePN. Kana iyo voltage iri pasi iyi miganhu yezviyo iri mune yakanyanya impedance nyika uye kana iyo voltage yakakwira ivo vanozove vari mune yekuparara mamiriro inova iri mhando yeasina-mitsara mudziyo.
Zvimiro
1. Varistor voltage (47V-1200V)
2. Yakanaka isiri-linearity coefficient
3. Yakakura inomira yekuwedzera ikozvino
4. Nguva yekupindura: <20ns
5. Dhayamita: 05D, 07D, 10D, 14D, 20D, 32D, 34S
Zvishandiso
* Transistor, diode, IC, thyristor kana triac semiconductor dziviriro.
* Kuchengetedzwa kwekudzivirira mumagetsi emutengi.
* Kuchengetedzwa kwekudzivirira mumagetsi emagetsi.
* Kuchengetedzwa kwekudzivirira mumagetsi emagetsi emidziyo, gasi uye peturu mafuta zvishandiso.
* Kudzoreredza uye electromagnetic vharuvhu yekuwedzera kutora.
Magadzirirwo
Main Magadzirirwo: 07D / 14D / 20D / 32D / 34S

Kune rumwe rutivi, Android ndeye OS inochinjika kune akasiyana madhizaini nemidziyo, izvi nekuda kwe "open source" hunhu. Kunyange Panguva iyo Google yakaratidza "rudo" rwayo rweRISC-V panguva ye "RISC-V Summit 2022" yakaitwa muna Zvita uye yakataura zvinangwa zvayo zve
... (1175 chars skipped) ... 
yakasimbiswa Android mudziyo inotakura ine kernel yakavakirwa pane rimwe reaya matavi eGKI, sezvo Google isiri kutsigira Android zvishandiso zvakavakwa neiyo mainline Linux kernel.
Neizvi, chaizvoizvoIyo inotevera vhezheni yeAndroid inoshandisa yazvino vhezheni yeGKI haizoenderane nayo midziyo ine machipisi RISC-V. Nekuda kweizvozvo, makambani arikuda kugadzira vhezheni yeAndroid yeRISC-V zvishandiso anozoda kuvandudza nekuchengetedza yavo yega yeLinux kernel vachishandisa RISC-V ACK zvigamba.

Sangano revarimi reCommercial Farmers’ Union, CFU, rinoti zvinhu hazvisati zvagadzikana mumapurazi kubva pakashanywa nechikwata chaitungamirirwa nemutevedzeri wemutungamiri wehurumende, VaArthur Mutambara.
Sangano iri rinoti pamapurazi mazana mana asara achiri mumaoko evarimi ava, anodarika zana acho akatopindwa zvechisimba.
CFU inoti haioni chirongwa cheLand Audit, chekuda kuziva mamiriro akaita zvinhu mumapurazi uye kuti ndianaani vane mapurazi, chichibudirira kana hurumende yemubatanidzwa isina kutanga yamisa mhirizhonga iri kuitika mumapurazi.
VaRenson Gasela ndivo munyori wezvekurima muMDC inotungamirirwa naVaArthur Mutambara.
VaGasela vaudza Jonga Kandemiiri weStudio7 kuti hurumende inofanirwa kutanga yamisa mhirizhonga iri mumapurazi isati yaita ongororo yayo.

Nyaya yekunyorwa kwebumbiro idzva remitero yenyika yambosendekwa parutivi nenyaya yegakava rinotyisa pakati pehurumende nevari kupa rubatsiro kuburikidza neboka reUNDP muHarare.
Zvinonzi UNDP haisi kunyatsofara nemafambisirwo ari kuitwa hurongwa hwekunyorwa kwebumbiro remitemo.
Asi bato reZanu-PF rinoti masangano anopa rubatsiro aya ave kuda kuisa maoko awo akasviba mukunyorwa kwebumbiro iri.
Mumwe wemasachigaro ekomiti yeparamende iri kuona nezvekunyorwa kwebumbiro idzva remitemo, VaPaul Mangwana, vakamirira Zanu-PF, vanoti ichokwadi kuti vambomisa chirongwa ichi sezvo paine kusawirirana nevari kubatsira nemari muchirongwa ichi.
VaTapuwa Mudambanuki ndivo Executive Director veAfrican Centre for Law and Justice. VaMudambanuki vanoti panofanirwa kuva nemushandira pamwe mukunyora bumbiro idzva remitemo yenyika.

izvo zvichaita kuti zvive nyore kune vashandisi kubata yavo mobile network yekubatanidza.Sekureva kweaimbova mupepeti weXDA Media-mukuru-Mishaal Rahman,

SIM kadhi slot.Iyi nhau inotsigirwa nekupihwa kwePixel 8 yakaburitswa neOnLeaks, inoratidza kuti hapana yakachengetwa SIM slot kuruboshwe,
zvichiratidza kuti iyo modhi nyowani ichave eSIM.
Yakawanda inotakurika, yakachengeteka uye inochinjika kupfuura yechinyakare makadhi emuviri, eSIM inogona kutsigira akawanda anotakura uye akawanda manhamba efoni, uye vashandisi vanogona kutenga.
uye shandisa ivo online.Parizvino, kusanganisira Apple, Samsung uye vamwe vagadziri venharembozha vakatangisa eSIM nharembozha, neiyo
kufambira mberi kwevagadziri venharembozha, kufarirwa kweSIM kunotarisirwa kuwedzera zvishoma nezvishoma, uye indasitiri inobatana ichaunza
kukurumidza kubuda.

Mumwedzi ichangopfuura basa rakawanda rakaitwa pa Dominican Republic kuvandudza kugona kuburitsa simba rinowedzerwazve uye panguva ino kuwedzera kuri kutora nzvimbo kwakakosha chaizvo kuitira kuti mune ramangwana huwandu hwese hwevanhu huve nesimba kubva kuzvisikwa uye nharaunda inogona kunge isina kusvibiswa.
Chaizvoizvo, basa riri kuitwa kusimudzira kushandiswa kwesimba rezuva uye simba remhepo, zvinova izvo zvinogona kugadzirwa zviri nyore uye muhuwandu hwakawanda panguva ino, saka kune mhando mbiri simba rinowedzeredzwa yakakosha kwazvo mune yazvino uye mune ramangwana re Dominican Republic, nyika inoteedzera zvakasara kuti zviwane chigadzirwa kuti chikwanise kupa vese vagari simba ravanoda vachishandisa zvinowedzerwazve masosi.
Nyika ino iri kuvandudza zvakanyanya mune izvi uye mumakore anotevera zvinotarisirwa kuti chikamu chakanaka chesimba rakadyiwa munyika yese chichauya chaicho kubva kusimba rezuva nemhepo.
Zvegore rino Dominican Republic uchave nemukana wekuita mamwe mapurojekiti ekuramba uchiwedzera huwandu hwe simba rezuva rakawanikwa uye zvakare zvine chekuita nesimba remhepo, maviri akakosha uye akawandisa simba munyika, kunyanya kunzvimbo dzakasiyana. Sezvazvinowanzoitika mune dzimwe nzvimbo dzepasi, kudyara mari kunowanzo kuve kwakakosha kuitira kuti mapurojekiti agone kuitwa uye kugadzirwa kwesimba rinowedzerwazve zvakawandisa kunogona kuwedzera zvishoma nezvishoma, mune ino kesi muDominican Republic.

2022 igore remakumi matatu rekutanga kwehukama hwekudyidzana pakati peChina neTajikistan.Pasi pehutungamiri hwe "Belt and Road" mutemo, SHINE yakatumira maion chromatographs kuTajikistan.Panguva ino, Li Sai, mainjiniya epashure-kutengesa eSHINE akaenda kuTajikistan kunogadzirisa midziyo yekuvaka marabhoritari evanhu veko uye kuchengetedza hutano hwekudya hweTajikistan.
Pashure pekutamiswa kunoverengeka, Li Sai nevamwe vakazosvika kuTajikistan na4:00 mangwanani musi wa15 Gumiguru.
Pazuva rechipiri mushure mekupinda muTajikistan, Li Sai akanzwa kusagadzikana nekuda kwekujairana kwake.Nekudaro, basa mushure mekupinda mushongwe rakanyanya, uye zvinodikanwa kuunganidza matafura nemacheya, kuisa zviridzwa, uye debug dzidziso.Kuti asakanganisa kufambira mberi kwebasa, Li Sai akasimbirira kushanda pabasa rake.Zviratidzo zvefivha zvakagara kwevhiki, uye Li Sai akapedzisawo basa rake akabudirira.
Rabhoritari muTajikistan haina chinhu, uye kune nzvimbo shoma dzokudyira.Kuti uchengetedze nguva uye upedze basa nekukurumidza, Li Sai aingove nekudya kaviri mangwanani nemanheru.Masikati, akatsungirira nzara uye akaramba achishanda.
Pashure pemavhiki maviri ebasa rinopfuurira, Li Sai nevamwe vakazopedza basa racho.Vatengi veTajik vakatenda Li Sai.
Panguva ino, semumiriri wemidziyo yemumba, SHINE zvigadzirwa zvinoratidza nyika simba remidziyo yemumba uye shanu-nyeredzi sevhisi yeSHINE.Masevhisi haana miganhu!
Nguva yekutumira: Nov-11-2022

Mitambo mizhinji iyi yainyorwa naEnock Chihombori.

Gringo akange arimo mufirimu rinonzi Yellow Card. Mumashoko kuvatori venhau, gurukota rinoona nezvekuburitswa kwemashoko Amai Monica Mutsvagwa vati nyika yarasikiwa negamba munyaya dzemitambo. Gringo asiya vana nanomwe nemudzimai, Netsai.

21 octobre 2022Biographie
Paule Boffa-Comby akatanga basa rake mumapoka makuru asati agadzira "ReThink & Lead" muna 2005, kambani yekudzidzisa uye yekutsigira matambudziko uye shanduko inoshanda nevakuru vakuru uye Comex yemasangano makuru (CAC 40 uye SBF120) , muFrance uye kunze kwenyika. Munyori wemabhuku akati wandei akadhindwa uye nhoroondo (Les Echos, HBR.fr), iye zvakare arikutsvakwa mutauri. Muna 2014, akatanga netiweki yevatungamiriri uye anovaunza pamwechete nguva nenguva kuti vataure nezve manejimendi, mubatanidzwa, manejimendi edambudziko, kusiyana, shanduko yemaitiro ekushanda.

R&D

Indasitiri-dzidzo Kubatanidzwa Chikoro-bhizinesi Kubatana
Veyong yakasaina chibvumirano chechikoro-bhizinesi chakakwana chekubatana neNortheast Agricultural University (NEAU), uye vakabatana vakagadzira chikoro-bhizinesi reR&D nzvimbo uye rabhoritari yakabatana neVeyong Group kuita tsvakiridzo yemishonga yezvipfuyo nekusimudzira, kusimudzira shanduko yetsvakiridzo yemishonga yezvipembenene. mhedzisiro, inosimudzira zvakakwana hutano hwemhuka nekuchengetedza chikafu, uye kusimudzira mhuka mhenyu kukurumidza kudzoreredza kugadzirwa.
Mukuru weHebei Agricultural University uye vanopfuura makumi matanhatu vadzidzi vechidiki kubva kuDhipatimendi reChemistry vakauya kuVeyong Pharmaceutical kuzoshanya nekuchinjana, uye hwaro hwekudzidzisa hweFaculty of Science yeHebei Agricultural University hwakanyorwa ipapo.Ichawedzera kudzamisa kudyidzana kwechikoro-bhizinesi neVeyong Pharmaceutical, kuumba indasitiri yehunyanzvi inosimudzira mumwe nemumwe, uye inosimudzira kukunda-kukunda mamiriro pakati peindasitiri nedzidzo.

Asiwo kune dzimwe nzira dzokurapa dzinopesana nezvinodiwa neBhaibheri. Isu hatishandisi nzira dzakadaro. Somuenzaniso, hatibvumi kuwedzerwa ropa nokuti Bhaibheri rinorambidza kudya ropa. (Mabasa 15:20) Bhaibheri rinoshorawo kurapwa pachishandiswa zvemidzimu.—VaGaratiya 5:19-21.
Asi kune nzira dzakawanda dzokurapwa nadzo dzisingapesani nezvinotaurwa neBhaibheri. Asi munhu nemunhu ndiye anozvisarudzira kurapwa kwaachada kuitwa. Mumwe muKristu anogona kubvuma kurapwa pachishandiswa imwe nzira asiwo mumwe muKristu oona hana yake isingamutenderi kurapwa pachishandiswa nzira iyoyo.—VaGaratiya 6:5.

Masangano akazvimirira oga achitungamirwa neCrisis in Zimbabwe Coalition ayambira kuti muZimbabwe mungangodeuka ropa rakawanda gore rinouya kana kukaitwa sarudzo African Union isina kupindira.
Mashoko aya ataurwa kumusangano weAU uri kuitirwa muKampala, kuUganda.
Vatungamiri venyika dzemuAfrica vari kutarisirwa kutanga kusangana neMuvhuro kuti vazeye nyaya dzakaita serunyararo muAfrica, mhando dzemoto uye nyaya dzechikafu. Makurukota ezvekudyidzana nedzimwe nyika nemakurukota ezvemitemo akatotanga kusangana kuUganda.
Zanu-PF inoti iri kuda kuti paitwe sarudzo gore rinouya sezvo hurumende yemubatanidzwa isiri kushanda zvakanaka. MDC inodawo kuti sarudzo idzi dziitwe nenzira yakachena, uye mitemo yesarudzo yavandudzwa. Masangano akazvimirira atanga nekuita musangano neChishanu, uyo wapindwa nevamiriri vehurumende dzakawanda.
Masangano aya anoti AU neSADC hadzina zvakawanda zvadziri kuita kugadzirisa zvinhu muZimbabwe. Vati Zanu-PF iri kuregererwa ichiita madiro ajojina. VaArnold Tsunga ndivo mukuru weInternational Commission of Jurists mudunhu reAfrica. VaTsunga vanoti vatungamiri vemuAfrica havafanire kupeta maoko Zimbabwe ichitsva.

Shenzhen Shuihuan-MBR Co. Ltd inogadzira michina yekuchenesa mvura yeMBR. Isu tinopa yakasanganiswa MBR yekurasa tsvina michina ine PVDF mhango fiber membrane zviyero, ayo anoshandiswa zvakanyanya kurapa maindasitiri uye matunhu emakanzura, zvakaita sewewage kubva kuzvipatara, mahotera, misha, mataundi, nzvimbo dzekudzidzisa, nzvimbo dzinoyevedza zvichingodaro.
Shenzhen SH-MBR Co. Ltd iri muShenzhen, guta razvino uno muChina. Tine mafekitori maviri ekugadzira iyo MBR yakasanganiswa yemidziyo yekurapa yemvura uye isina mhango fiber membrane ma module. Imwe fekitori iri iripo in Liaoning dunhu uye imwe iri Dunhu reJiangxi. Isu tine anopfuura makore gumi nematanhatu 'ruzivo muMBR kurapwa kwemvura yakasviba. We inopa kurapwa kweseweji, kuisirwa, kubvunza, kuvimbisa, kuyedza uye kugadzirisa kuona kuramba kuchitevedza.
Tiri kutsvaga boka rekunze kwekuchengetedzwa kwezvakatipoteredza uye indasitiri yekurapa mvura yakasviba vanhu vakakurumbira mukudyidzana kwakabatana. Isu tinopa yakazara seti yezvigadzirwa tekinoroji rutsigiro, kugadzirwa, mushandirapamwe, uye pamwe chete kuvaka chigadziko chekugadzira.
